metadata.name: Thankful, Grateful, and Kind
metadata.description: This is from a collaboration from 2021 during a pandemic road trip to Kentucky. between my partner and I. Upon purchasing this NFT you have the option to have it printed or hold onto only the digital file. The digital file is held for artistic value. Only 7 prints will be allowed for every NFT.  If you do not have the image printed, you will get airdropped images at a later date.
